short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically switches to the next tab every few seconds

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tab Switcher is a Chrome extension that automatically switches between open tabs at a specified interval. With the ability to set a custom time interval for switching, this extension helps users efficiently navigate through their open tabs without wasting time or energy. The extension also includes a pop-up page with toggle buttons for easy on/off switching and the ability to customize the delay setting. Whether you're juggling multiple tabs for work or leisure, Tab Switcher helps streamline your browsing experience and boost productivity.
